export const lightTheme = {
  body: "#fafafa",
  primaryColor: "#FF7082",
  secondaryColor: "#A064A0",
  example: "#db7093",
  synonyms: "#648CF6",
  section: {
    background:
      "linear-gradient(151deg,rgba(234, 239, 255, 1) 34%,rgba(208, 213, 252, 1) 100%)",
    border: "none",
    boxShadow: "0 10px 6px -6px #777",
  },
  text: "#363537",
  toggleBorder: "#A7BEE0",
  gradient:
    "linear-gradient(to top, #030303, #0d0d0d, #141414, #1a1a1a, #202020)",
  background: "#fafafa",
};

export const darkTheme = {
  body: "#333",
  primaryColor: "#806C97",
  secondaryColor: "#EAEFFF",
  section: {
    background: "#333",
    border: "#fafafa",
    boxShadow: "none",
  },
  example: "#D0D5FC",
  synonyms: "#cecece",
  text: "#FAFAFA",
  toggleBorder: "#F8D027",
  gradient:
    "linear-gradient(to top, #030303, #0d0d0d, #141414, #1a1a1a, #202020)",
  background: "#333",
};
